flowchart TD
  subgraph Requirement[需求领域]
    Card[CardAggregate]
    Card -->|事件| Pipeline
  end
  subgraph Pipeline[流水线领域]
    PipelineAgg[PipelineAggregate]
    PipelineAgg -->|阶段事件| Agent
  end
  subgraph Agent[智能体领域]
    Task[TaskAggregate]
    Task -->|端口| ClonePool
    Task -->|端口| AIRuntime
    Task -->|日志| LogFile
    Task -->|检索| Knowledge
  end
  subgraph Knowledge[知识库领域]
    Document[Document]
    Document -->|检索| Agent
  end
  subgraph ClonePool[克隆池领域]
    ClonePoolInst[ClonePool]
    ClonePoolInst -->|实例| Agent
  end
  subgraph AIRuntime[AI运行时领域]
    Provider[Provider]
    Provider -->|模型| Agent
  end
  subgraph Project[项目领域]
    ProjectEnt[Project]
    ProjectEnt -->|配置| Requirement
  end
  subgraph Git[Git领域]
    Repository[Repository]
    Repository -->|PR/MR| Agent
    Repository -->|分支| Project
  end
  subgraph Notify[通知领域]
    Notification[Notification]
    Notification -->|推送| User[用户]
    Notification <-->|事件| Requirement
    Notification <-->|事件| Pipeline
    Notification <-->|事件| Agent
    Notification <-->|事件| ClonePool
    Notification <-->|事件| AIRuntime
    Notification <-->|事件| Project
    Notification <-->|事件| Git
  end
